I think it has something do with with the `@AutoConfigureAfter({ JtaAutoConfiguration.class, JndiConnectionFactoryAutoConfiguration.class })` annotation in `ActiveMQAutoConfiguration`.

We have a workaround by standing up our own with:

``` java
